 <text>
  <front>
   <head>To Adversity.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">HAIL, pallid nymph, with downcast eye,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">With sable garb, and head reclin'd,</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Severely kind Adversity,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Preceptress of the thoughtless mind!</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">'Tis thine to draw dark Error's veil</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">From the deluded eyes of youth;</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">To teach the heart of Pride to feel,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And lead the wanderer to Truth.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="sestarima">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Though venal Flattery and Deceit</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Ne'er offer incense at thy shrine,</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Pity still seeks thy lone retreat,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And real Friendship still is thine.</l>
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">For, as pure gold by fire we prove,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Adversity's the test of love.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
